tspan.tspan: We heartily welcome contributions from students and faculty members, irrespective of affiliation. The portals for submitting
all kinds of content can be found on our website. More specific details regarding the content can also be found there, so

text.tspan: please take a close look at the linked page if you are interested in contributing.

tspan.tspan: : We publish write-ups on interesting ideas in science, as long as the content is accessible to a broader

text.tspan: audience and not just to the experts. Submit your articles here.

tspan.tspan: : In order to showcase the frontiers of research, we publish short summaries (350-400 words) of recently
published science research articles. The summary should broadly lay out the questions being asked and the new results

text.tspan: obtained. Submit your research stories here.

tspan.tspan: : We also feature science games such as crosswords, quizzes and word-link games. If you have content

text.tspan: for these games or have new interesting games in mind, please send them our way.

tspan.tspan: If want us to interview specific scientific personalities or if you have an interview that you

text.tspan: want to publish, please get in touch with us.
Submissions are accepted on a rolling basis, so send in your content whenever you are ready.

tspan.tspan: We are currently looking to expand our team. If you are interested in what we do and are confident that you will be able to
devote time to this, please reach out to us at scicomm@iiserkol.ac.in. We will be happy to discuss possible roles for you
